<h3>setGallerySize</h3>

<p>Sets the height of the gallery to the height of the tallest cell. Enabled by default <code><span class="comment">setGallerySize: true</span></code>.</p>

<p>Use <code>setGallerySize: <span class="literal">false</span></code> if you prefer to size the gallery with CSS, rather than using the size of cells.</p>

<div class="duo example">
  <div class="duo__cell example__code">
    ``` js
    setGallerySize: false
    ```

    ``` css
    /* gallery height */
    .gallery {
      height: 160px;
    }

    /* cell inherit height from gallery */
    .gallery-cell {
      height: 100%;
    }
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="duo__cell example__demo">
    <div class="gallery gallery--set-gallery-size-disabled js-flickity"
      data-flickity-options='{ "setGallerySize": false }'>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
    </div>
    {{#codepens.set_gallery_size_disabled}}
      {{>edit_demo}}
    {{/codepens.set_gallery_size_disabled}}
  </div>
</div>

<p>You can size the gallery height as percentage of its width with <code><span class="attribute">padding-bottom</span></code> and <code><span class="class">.flickity-viewport</span></code> CSS.</p>

<div class="duo example">
  <div class="duo__cell example__code">
    ``` js
    setGallerySize: false
    ```

    ``` css
    /* gallery height, as percentage of width */
    .gallery {
      padding-bottom: 33.3%;
    }

    /* viewport inherit size from gallery */
    .gallery .flickity-viewport {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* cell inherit height from gallery */
    .gallery-cell {
      height: 100%;
    }
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="duo__cell example__demo">
    <div class="gallery gallery--set-gallery-size-disabled-percentage js-flickity"
